             was indicted for <rs id="t17910608-24-off141" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17910608-24-off141" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910608-24-off141" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910608-24-cd142" type="crimeDate">20th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910608-24-off141 t17910608-24-cd142"></join>, one boiling copper, value 10 s. belonging to 
                     
                        <persName id="t17910608-24-victim287" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Mortimer
                        <interp inst="t17910608-24-victim287" type="surname" value="Mortimer"></interp>
